description.desc: Increase all players' stats within a party by certain percentage

description.name: Bahamut

description.name: Infinity

description.desc: Temporarily protects all party members from abnormal conditions.
description.name: Holy Shield

description.desc: Attacks a single monster with a holy arrow, incurring tremendous holy damage.

description.name: Genesis

description.desc: Enables one to shrug off abnormal conditions. The higher the skill level, the more types of abnormal conditions one can nullify.
description.name: Hero's Will
